","tid":37742,"uid":55069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:51:23.000Z","msg":"識打邊爐一定係搵間任食任飲啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同一大班兄弟食唔洗就住就住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d04c2f4e982d48bb558700c8e17604c36faf0a","tid":37742,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:32:57.000Z","msg":"零負評高質潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe1968df79909aa95f175e49e2d682b0ecf10e5","tid":37742,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:37:18.000Z","msg":"睇到個標題嚇到叫左出黎，老細問咩事，我照讀比佢聽，讀左標題內文都未開始讀，佢成塊面白哂，自言自語，猛咁話「共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生；共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&hellip;&hellip;」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲「鳴呀，點解係我」就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切，有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到變左弱智，不停問人要唔要食腸仔蛋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就好好彩無咩事，但同班同事五十幾個人即時變左失業，你條仆街真係害人害物&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30710e80d7616cc0726a130afacd674d02e222c2","tid":37742,"uid":44487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:42:39.000Z","msg":"睇極都係咁正 <br />\n過兩日又準備同成班毒撚圍爐取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85769dcbc410dfaaf7897e47416d891ee596a837","tid":37742,"uid":57695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:44:45.000Z","msg":"55 ching ho ball"},{"pid":"96c57691c76feb5897d34efdb24afd0c18aaa4f7","tid":37742,"uid":50795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:46:06.000Z","msg":"睇返篇潮文，即刻約班fd聽晚打邊爐先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777fee348877ff0cde1d2a34c152d9c51643ae64","tid":37742,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike"